{"product_id":"madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-shampoo-250ml","title":"MÁDARA Gloss and Vibrancy shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGently cleanse and protect the hair with this shine–enhancing and volume-boosting shampoo. Formulated with Northern Birch and Cranberry, it ensures stronger, silkier and shinier hair. Plus, this shampoo is packaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle to reduce the volume of new plastic bottles made each year!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently massage into wet hair. Lather and rinse with water. For best results, use in combination with MÁDARA Gloss And Vibrancy Conditioner.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Coco-glucoside, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Citric acid, Sodium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Aroma, Behenyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract, Brassica Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917168873799,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-shampoo-250ml-798928.jpg?v=1739897192","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-gloss-and-vibrancy-shampoo-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}